name: RAYBESTOS MANHATTAN COMPANY v. MILFORD AUTO PARTS, INC.
name_abbreviation: Raybestos Manhattan Co. v. Milford Auto Parts, Inc.

parties: RAYBESTOS MANHATTAN COMPANY v. MILFORD AUTO PARTS, INC.

opinions.text:
ORDER
Treating the plaintiffs motion to affirm the judgment of the Superior Court as a motion to dismiss this appeal as premature, the motion to dismiss is granted.
SHEA, J., did not participate.

attorneys: Winograd, Shine & Zacks, P.C., E. Martin Stutchfield, Providence, for plaintiff.
Laurent C. Bilodeau, Woonsocket, for defendant.

RAYBESTOS MANHATTAN COMPANY v. MILFORD AUTO PARTS, INC.
